casebody.head_matter:
In re Gregory C. KAPORDELIS, petitioner.
No. 16-6434.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 7, 2016.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of habeas corpus dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
